SimulationControl,
  No,                                     !- Do Zone Sizing Calculation
  No,                                     !- Do System Sizing Calculation
  No,                                     !- Do Plant Sizing Calculation
  No,                                     !- Run Simulation for Sizing Periods
  Yes,                                    !- Run Simulation for Weather File Run Periods
